{"ID":"20260605151007-27o7wnb","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605151007-27o7wnb","title":"2021年天津卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605151022-6tcj78c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151022-6tcj78c","updated":"20260605151022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"念奴娇"}]},{"ID":"20260605151022-l35utpb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151022-l35utpb","updated":"20260605151022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用傅安道和朱希真梅词韵"}]},{"ID":"20260605151022-nbna4mn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151022-nbna4mn","updated":"20260605151022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"[宋]朱熹"}]},{"ID":"20260605151022-80xuk8z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151022-80xuk8z","updated":"20260605151022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"临风一笑，问群芳、谁是真香纯白？独立无朋，算只有、姑射"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"注"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"山头仙客。绝艳谁怜，真心自保，邈与尘缘隔。天然殊胜，不关风露冰雪。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151022-im3nomg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151022-im3nomg","updated":"20260605151022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应笑俗李粗桃，无言翻引得、狂蜂轻蝶。争似黄昏闲弄影，清浅一溪霜月。画角吹残，瑶台梦断，直下成休歇。绿阴青子，莫教容易披折。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151022-yq3c9ne","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151022-yq3c9ne","updated":"20260605151022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"[注]姑射：神话中的山名，神仙所居之处。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151007-y19goiq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151007-y19goiq","updated":"20260605151035"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605151035-g3wfnzq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151035-g3wfnzq","updated":"20260605151035"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．下列对这首词的理解和赏析，不恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605151035-nj9np4k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151035-nj9np4k","updated":"20260605151035"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．“和”，即和韵，是诗词写作的一种方式。这首词就是朱熹依照傅安道和朱希真梅花词的韵而创作的。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151035-hn8mvnv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151035-hn8mvnv","updated":"20260605151035"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．词的开篇运用拟人手法，并以问句提起，将梅花与“群芳”比较，突出梅花的清香与洁白。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151035-mwtrgvd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151035-mwtrgvd","updated":"20260605151035"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．词中写梅花美艳无比，与姑射山仙人相伴；“风露冰雪”的考验赋予了梅花不同寻常的韵致。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151035-5vo3omm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151035-5vo3omm","updated":"20260605151035"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．“画角”“绿阴”数句，写梅花宁愿休歇凋零，也不愿结出青青的梅子而被人折断梅枝。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151035-lsoz5wu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151035-lsoz5wu","updated":"20260605151035"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．“黄昏闲弄影，清浅一溪霜月”描绘了怎样的画面？"}]},{"ID":"20260605151035-dyyytol","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151035-dyyytol","updated":"20260605151035"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．请指出词人借梅花寄托了怎样的理想人格。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151007-x2eavdv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151007-x2eavdv","updated":"20260605151045"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605151045-3c5e13y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151045-3c5e13y","updated":"20260605151045"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．C    15．黄昏时分，梅花闲展芳姿，月色清凉，倒映在澄莹的溪水中。描绘了一幅清雅幽静的画面。    16．天性高洁，保持本心，特立独行，不同流俗。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151007-rzgic70","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151007-rzgic70","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-4hnudxg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-4hnudxg","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14．本题考查学生对诗歌的综合理解和赏析能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-ju9jytj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-ju9jytj","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“‘风露冰雪’的考验赋予了梅花不同寻常的韵致”错。“天然殊胜，不关风露冰雪”意思是梅花的高洁风致是天然生成，与风露冰雪无关。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-4tk5kyv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-4tk5kyv","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-1vars15","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-1vars15","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"15．本题考查学生对诗歌景物形象及画面的鉴赏能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-lnabhc2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-lnabhc2","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“黄昏闲弄影，清浅一溪霜月”，描写黄昏时分，梅花面对清浅的溪水临水弄影，清清溪水倒影着天上一轮明月，和梅花的倩影构成绝美的图景。此句选择梅花、清溪和霜月为意象，描绘梅花倒影在溪水中的芳姿，整个画面清幽雅致，澄澈人心。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-ny57pa6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-ny57pa6","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"16．本题考查学生鉴赏诗歌形象与评价诗歌中作者的思想情感的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-bose79u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-bose79u","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"诗歌描写梅花在群芳中保持“真香纯白”，只有姑射山头的仙人能与之为伍，并说梅花天性高洁，与风霜冰雪无关，写出梅花的天性高洁；"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-g7vrjn1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-g7vrjn1","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"再写梅花“真心自保，邈与尘缘隔”，为了保持自己的高洁本心，宁可远远离开尘世，与那污浊的尘世保持距离，写出梅花的保持本心，不同流俗。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-pyamcs7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-pyamcs7","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"诗歌用俗李粗桃衬托梅花的高洁，那些俗艳的花朵争奇斗艳，招蜂引蝶；而梅花却在明月的陪伴下在清澈的溪水中映照芳姿，写出梅花的保持本心，特立独行，不同流俗。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151058-6fevwn9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151058-6fevwn9","updated":"20260605151058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"梅花的品格就是诗人的理想品格。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151007-uu9gzy6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151007-uu9gzy6","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}